dc_description_s: AMS 1. North Decimal Degree 23.483333. South Decimal Degree 23.450000. East Decimal Degree 120.450000. West Decimal Degree 120.383333. Alternate title: Kagi. In upper left margin: Fomosa city plans 1:10,000. Polyconic projection. Relief shown by 10 meter contour intervals and spot elevations. Compiled from aerial photography dated January 1999, by photo-planimetric method and by reference to Formosa 1:50,000, A.M.S. Sheet 2117-II, 1944; Japanese Imperial Land Survey, Kagi, 1928; Town Plan of Kagi 1:11,000 (approx)., OSS, 1944; Town Plan of Kagi (Japanese Source), 1935. Additional information from intelligence data. Place names are transcribed according to the modified Hepburn (Romaji) System.
dc_publisher_s: Washington, D.C. : Army Map Service, U.S. Army, 1945.
